  <div class="views-field views-field-created">        <span class="field-content date">27 Nov 2017</span>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Elephant Insurance, the Henrico-based direct-to consumer insurance specialist, is pleased to announce Alberto Schiavon as its new CEO.<br /><br />Schiavon, 31, has worked for the Admiral Group, Elephant’s parent company headquartered in the UK for the last five years in number of senior positions. Schiavon, originally from Venice, Italy, joined the Group in 2012 as an International Pricing Manager. More recently he has been UK Director of Sales and Marketing. Schiavon moved to Richmond in March 2017 to head up Marketing and Pricing.<br /></p></div>  </div>  
